{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":1,"day":12}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"怀念周总理","authors":["莫文骅"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"声威震人寰，功勋著世间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步旅劈荆棘，舟行过险滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简朴常自励，茹苦共民艰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥神若定，运筹掌中看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秉性极刚毅，处事精且细。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堪称卓越才，领袖倍重器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奸贼“四人帮”，万般施毒技。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生时狠摧残，死后尤妒忌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品德洁如玉，功高不夸诩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨灰洒满天，顿成倾盆雨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逝世一周年，耳犹闻教语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设装甲兵，红旗必高举！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}